text: Jochen Neuling (born 10 February 1938) is a West German rower who represented the United Team of Germany. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics in Rome with the men's coxless pair where they came fourth. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:West German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United Team of Germany Category:Rowers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Rohrberg
